  "root_text": {
    "sn14.18:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 14.18 ",
    "sn14.18:0.2": "2. Dutiyavagga ",
    "sn14.18:0.3": "Assaddhamūlakasutta ",
    "sn14.18:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṁ viharati. ",
    "sn14.18:1.2": "“Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.18:1.3": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:1.4": "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:1.5": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:1.6": "saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:1.7": "hirimanā hirimanehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:1.8": "paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.18:1.9": "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandiṁsu samiṁsu …pe… ",
    "sn14.18:1.10": "anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandissanti samessanti …pe…. ",
    "sn14.18:2.1": "Etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṁ addhānaṁ dhātusova sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.18:2.2": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:2.3": "ahirikā ahirikehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti, duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:2.4": "saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:2.5": "hirimanā hirimanehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:2.6": "paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samentīti. ",
    "sn14.18:3.1": "Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṁsandanti samenti. ",
    "sn14.18:3.2": "Assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:3.3": "anottappino anottappīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:3.4": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:3.5": "saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:3.6": "ottappino ottappīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:3.7": "paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti …pe… ",
    "sn14.18:3.8": "paṭhamavāro viya vitthāretabbo. ",
    "sn14.18:4.1": "Dhātusova, bhikkhave …pe… ",
    "sn14.18:4.2": "assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:4.3": "appassutā appassutehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:4.4": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:4.5": "saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; bahussutā bahussutehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti, paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti …pe…. ",
    "sn14.18:5.1": "Dhātusova, bhikkhave …pe… ",
    "sn14.18:5.2": "assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:5.3": "kusītā kusītehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:5.4": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:5.5": "saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:5.6": "āraddhavīriyā āraddhavīriyehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti …pe…. ",
    "sn14.18:6.1": "Dhātusova, bhikkhave …pe… ",
    "sn14.18:6.2": "assaddhā assaddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:6.3": "muṭṭhassatino muṭṭhassatīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:6.4": "duppaññā duppaññehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:6.5": "saddhā saddhehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; ",
    "sn14.18:6.6": "upaṭṭhitassatino upaṭṭhitassatīhi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samenti; paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṁ saṁsandanti samentī”ti …pe…. ",
    "sn14.18:6.7": "Aṭṭhamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn14.18:0.1": "Linked Discourses 14.18 ",
    "sn14.18:0.2": "Chapter Two ",
    "sn14.18:0.3": "Beginning With the Faithless ",
    "sn14.18:1.1": "At Sāvatthī. ",
    "sn14.18:1.2": "“Mendicants, sentient beings join together and converge because of an element: ",
    "sn14.18:1.3": "the faithless with the faithless, ",
    "sn14.18:1.4": "the unconscientious with the unconscientious, ",
    "sn14.18:1.5": "the witless with the witless, ",
    "sn14.18:1.6": "the faithful with the faithful, ",
    "sn14.18:1.7": "the conscientious with the conscientious, ",
    "sn14.18:1.8": "and the wise with the wise. ",
    "sn14.18:1.9": "In the past … ",
    "sn14.18:1.10": "In the future … ",
    "sn14.18:2.1": "At present, too, sentient beings join together and converge because of an element. … ",
    "sn14.18:2.2": "",
    "sn14.18:2.3": "",
    "sn14.18:2.4": "",
    "sn14.18:2.5": "",
    "sn14.18:2.6": "",
    "sn14.18:3.1": "Sentient beings join together and converge because of an element: ",
    "sn14.18:3.2": "the faithless with the faithless, ",
    "sn14.18:3.3": "the imprudent with the imprudent, ",
    "sn14.18:3.4": "the witless with the witless, ",
    "sn14.18:3.5": "the faithful with the faithful, ",
    "sn14.18:3.6": "the prudent with the prudent, ",
    "sn14.18:3.7": "and the wise with the wise. ",
    "sn14.18:3.8": "(The following should be told in full like the first section.) ",
    "sn14.18:4.1": "Sentient beings come together because of an element: ",
    "sn14.18:4.2": "the faithless … ",
    "sn14.18:4.3": "unlearned … ",
    "sn14.18:4.4": "witless … ",
    "sn14.18:4.5": "the faithful … ",
    "sn14.18:5.1": "Sentient beings come together because of an element: ",
    "sn14.18:5.2": "the faithless … ",
    "sn14.18:5.3": "lazy … ",
    "sn14.18:5.4": "witless. ",
    "sn14.18:5.5": "the faithful … ",
    "sn14.18:5.6": "energetic … wise. ",
    "sn14.18:6.1": "Sentient beings come together because of an element: ",
    "sn14.18:6.2": "the faithless … ",
    "sn14.18:6.3": "unmindful … ",
    "sn14.18:6.4": "witless. ",
    "sn14.18:6.5": "the faithful … ",
    "sn14.18:6.6": "mindful … wise.” "
  },
